from collections import Counter

def around_fib(n):
    fib = [0, 1]
    while len(fib) < n:
        fib.append(fib[-1] + fib[-2])
    f = str(fib[n])
    digit_counts = Counter(f)
    (max_count, max_digit) = max(((v, -int(k)) for (k, v) in digit_counts.items()))
    last_chunk = f[-(len(f) % 25 or 25):]
    return f'Last chunk {last_chunk}; Max is {max_count} for digit {-max_digit}'
